It was up, no one else was there to contest the spawn, It is not a rotational spawn according to the posted list which is a list that everyone on the Rathe respects and I think we all appreciate this.<br>
So a bunch of people decided to get together and kill this difficult mob.<br>
All I am really interested in hearing is &quot;congratulations!&quot; or &quot;well done!&quot;.<br>
The rest of this topic is Mind numbing rhetoric and I really dont care to be told where I can and can not play this game.<br>
I was in Plane of Nightmares the other day and saw someone organize a Hedge flagging session with people that were in the zone. The first 18 people to join got to go. Whether they were successful or not is not the issue, what is the issue is why I dont see 22 pages of BS on the fact that 18 non-same guilded people attempted to do a flagging event!!!<br>
I would like to see tier 4 zones too you know. Seems to me like you guys are saying the only way that will ever happen is if I join one of the guilds that currently goes to those zones.<br>
So what say you BoTS, NB, TL?..Care to recruit about 2500 level 60-65 characters so that they too, can see beyond the zones where &quot;That sort&quot; can play?<br>
Otherwise STFU and let people play this game since they have not broken any of the damn rules.<br>
<br>
Tired of this crap.<br>
