<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr><br>
This is classic High level guild members talking penalties on teaming on NON ROTATIONAL Mobs, hehe like thier members never got together with other guilds members to bust Gore or one of the other non-rotational mobs. <br>
<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
